---
import Navigation from "../components/Navigation.astro";
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";

const lastModifiedDate = new Date().toLocaleString("en-GB");
---

<Layout>
  <div class="page-wrapper">
    <div class="sticky-nav">
      <Navigation label="/Now" link="/now" />
    </div>
    <div class="content-wrapper">
      <div class="content-section">
        <div class="about-me section-style">
          <h2>About Me</h2>
          <p>
            Hi there! ðŸ‘‹ I'm Joe Sheen, a Software Engineer based in Bristol. I
            work at <a href="https://oceanbluesoftware.co.uk/" target="_blank"
              >Ocean Blue Software</a
            >, where I'm focused on developing a Kotlin-based automation tool
            and testing suite to validate smart TV software and applications
            before they're submitted for certification. As part of the team, I
            contribute to streamlining workflows, improving efficiency, and
            ensuring higher-quality products. Want to know more about my
            professional background? Check out my CV:
          </p>
          <div class="button-wrapper">
            <a
              href="/joseph_sheen_curriculum_vitae.pdf"
              target="_blank"
              class="cv-button">ðŸ“„ View My CV</a
            >
          </div>
          <p>
            Outside of work, I'm passionate about staying active, with running
            and gym workouts being my main focus. I also enjoy exploring
            Bristol's vibrant culture and experimenting with new technologies.
            In my downtime, you'll usually find me reading, listening to
            podcasts, or enjoying music. I love socialising and spending time
            with friends, whether it's grabbing a coffee of hanging out over the
            weekend. Weather it's tech, fitness, or personal growth, I'm always
            eager to learn and explore new areas.
          </p>
        </div>
        <!--div class="now section-style">
          <h2>/Now</h2>
        </div-->
        <div class="why-shoejs section-style">
          <h2>Why shoejs</h2>
          <p>
            My full first name is Joseph (but I prefer J<span class="name-span"
              >oe</span
            >), and my last name is <span class="name-span">Sh</span>een. Back
            at university, a course mate started call me "<span
              class="name-span">Shoe</span
            >" - a mashup of my first and last names. I liked it, so it stuck.
          </p>
          <p>
            Later on, I added "<span class="name-span">js</span>" to the end.
            Those are my initials, but also the file extension for JavaScript
            source code, which felt pretty fitting for a software engineer.
          </p>
          <p>
            When I was setting up this site, I wanted a domain that was short,
            unique, easy to share, and most importantly something I'd actually
            remember. After browsing around, I found that <span
              class="name-span">shoejs.co.uk</span
            > was not only available, but also cheaper than something like <span
              class="name-span">joesheen.co.uk</span
            >, so I went with it. Simple as that.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <hr class="horizontal-line" />
      <div class="date-modified">
        <span>
          Last Modified: <span>{lastModifiedDate}</span>
        </span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .sticky-nav {
    position: sticky;
    top: 0;
    z-index: 1000;
  }

  .section-style {
    border: solid;
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    border-color: var(--onyx);
  }

  .section-style p {
    padding: 0 15px 0 15px;
  }

  .about-me,
  .why-shoejs,
  .now {
    margin-top: 20px;
  }

  .button-wrapper {
    margin: 0 auto;
    width: fit-content;
    padding-bottom: 10px;
  }

  .cv-button {
    background-color: var(--onyx);
    color: var(--sandy-brown);
    border: none;
    padding: 12px 24px;
    font-size: 16px;
    text-decoration: none;
    border-radius: 8px;
    cursor: pointer;
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    transition:
      background-color 0.3s ease,
      transform 0.2s ease;
    font-family: "Segoe UI", Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
  }

  .cv-button:hover {
    background-color: var(--sandy-brown);
    color: var(--onyx);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  .name-span {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--tomato);
  }

  .horizontal-line {
    border: none;
    border-radius: 8px;
    height: 3px;
    background-color: var(--onyx);
    margin: 15px auto 5px auto;
  }

  .date-modified {
    text-align: right;
    padding-right: 5px;
    font-size: small;
  }
</style>
